title: Transcend Wide Carry-On Expandable Spinner - TU421VXSPW
description: The latest trend in carry-on luggage, the Transcend Wide-body Carry-On Expandable Spinner is an ideal choice for both switching between domestic and international travel. The shorter and wider configuration offers the maximum packing capacity and easily fits feet-first in the overhead compartment.  Transcend VX™ versatile expansion allows up to an extra 2.5" of customizable capacity and ensures a sturdy shape for easy packing.
